WEBVTT

00:01.814 --> 00:03.649
<i>So tell me how this works.</i>

00:03.683 --> 00:05.717
<i>I'm awake with my wife,</i>
<i>and I close my eyes,</i>

00:05.735 --> 00:08.070
<i>I open them,</i>
<i>I'm awake with my son.</i>

00:08.103 --> 00:10.572
And this has been happening
since the accident?

00:12.775 --> 00:14.726
<i>So you begin</i>
<i>working on one case</i>

00:14.744 --> 00:17.029
<i>here in reality,</i>
<i>and then suddenly</i>

00:17.063 --> 00:19.988
<i>you begin working another case</i>
<i>there in your dream.</i>

00:20.063 --> 00:22.176
<i>It all feels</i>
<i>completely real to me.</i>

00:22.228 --> 00:24.540
<i>You can't tell</i>
<i>whether you're awake or asleep</i>

00:24.604 --> 00:25.637
at this very moment?

00:25.672 --> 00:28.607
<i>Well, I can assure you,</i>
Detective Britten, this is not a dream.

00:28.641 --> 00:31.226
That's exactly
what the other shrink said.

