What was that you were saying
about the Westfield case?

02:32.711 --> 02:34.078
Sir?

02:34.112 --> 02:35.947
Just now, on the thing,
you were, you were...

02:35.965 --> 02:37.131
Were you talking
to someone else?

02:37.166 --> 02:38.483
You have your mic open or what?

02:38.517 --> 02:40.585
